comments: Jokic (DEN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Morant (MEM) at the end of his drive.
Brooks (MEM) briefly grasps Murray's (DEN) arm on the perimeter, and the contact is marginal.
Clarke (MEM) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Jokic's (DEN) upper body after his release, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) makes contact with Brooks' (MEM) arm after he gathers on his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Morris (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position as he moves alongside Morant's (MEM) path during the driving shot attempt.
Valanciunas (MEM) moves alongside Jokic's (DEN) path when marginal body contact occurs as he contests Jokic's driving shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) jumps vertically and cleanly blocks Jokic's (DEN) shot attempt prior to making incidental body contact.
Valanciunas (MEM) briefly grasps Jokic's (DEN) jersey during the rebound, and the contact is marginal.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a screening position in Morris' (DEN) path and absorbs the body contact.

Jokic (DEN) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position as he absorbs the body contact from Morant (MEM) during the driving shot attempt. The baseline official unnecessarily raises his arm in an attempt to signal verticality.
Brooks (MEM) delivers arm and body contact into Jokic (DEN), which affects his ability to maintain control of the ball.
